      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（最近さくら達は、レッスンの休憩中）\n（よくお笑いライブのDVDを観ているようだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Lately‚ Sakura and the others have taken to）\n（watching comedy show DVDs during their breaks.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あははははっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahahah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "お、お腹痛いよー！\n『ホットドッグさん』ホントおもしろいねっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-my stomach hurts from laughing!\nMr. Hotdog is so funny!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "このすっとぼけちゃってる感じが最高だよね～\nあ～お腹痛い……ふふふっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love how they play all innocent and dumb!\nPhew! My stomach hurts… Heheh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.933333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ねっ、雫ちゃんはどう？\nホットドッグさんのお笑い、好き？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Shizuku-chan‚ what do you think?\nDo you like Mr. Hotdog’s comedy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.200000000000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "…………うん、好き\nおもしろい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Yeah‚ I like it.\nIt’s funny.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……とは言うが、雫の表情に変化は見られない）\n（ 感情を表に出すのがとことん苦手なんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Despite her words‚ I don’t see any change in Shizuku’s expression.）\n（She really seems to struggle with expressing her emotions.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ雫、最近笑ったのっていつ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey Shizuku‚ when was the last time you laughed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.76666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……いま？\nお笑い見て、クスってなった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Just now.\nI smirked while watching the comedy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9500000476837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、そうじゃなくって\n声上げて笑って、笑顔になった時のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I mean\nwhen’s the last time you laughed out loud.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.31666671435036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……覚えてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "………I don’t remember.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.91666671435036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "表情筋が硬いのかな？\nちょっとごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe your facial muscles are stiff.\nHere‚ I’ll try something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.71666671435033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "うにゅ……さくら、ちゃん……\nほっぺた……や、めて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Erm… Sakura-chan…\nDon't……pull my……cheeks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.15000004768366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "こうして顔の筋肉を柔らかくして\n口の端っこを指で持ち上げて……はい、笑顔っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lemme just soften your facial muscles a little‚\nlift the corner of your mouth‚ and… there‚ a smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.75000004768366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……かわいい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh… So cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.21666671435032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん\nそんなふうに笑うんだね、雫ちゃんって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ yep!\nI didn’t know you smiled like that‚ Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0254875183105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……指\nもう離して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you remove…\n…your fingers now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.05882085164384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "あ……うん\nごめんね、痛かった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… yeah.\nSorry. Did it hurt?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7254875183105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "違う……けど、こんなことしても\n私、かわいく、ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… but you doing that\nwon’t make me cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2588208516438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない。ちゃんとかわいかったよ？\nだから雫ちゃんの自然な笑顔、見せてほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true. You looked really cute.\nI wish you’d show us your natural smile‚ Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3588208516438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "うん……できるのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder… if I can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.12106248764756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "焦らなくても大丈夫だよ\nみんなと一緒に、少しずつ練習していこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no need to rush.\nJust keep practicing bit by bit with the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.75843216805224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "……わかり、ました……\n……ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright.\n…I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.32509883471896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-3d",
      "startTime": 127.02509883471896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？\n……何してるんだ、千紗？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm?\nWhat’re you doing‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3584321680523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sneak-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 131.32509883471897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ひぅ！ ……{user}、さん？\nな、なんだ……びっくりしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek! {user}-san?\nPhew… You startled me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.45843216805252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "しーっ。あれ、見てください……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shhh. Over there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.15843216805257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（そこにいたのは、ヘッドホンをつけた雫だった）\n（テレビでアイドルのライブDVDを観ているらしい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I look to see Shizuku with her headphones on.）\n（It appears she’s watching a DVD of an idol live.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんの顔、よく見てください",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look carefully at Shizuku-chan’s face.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.65843216805257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "さっきからずーっと、あんな風に笑顔なんです\nなんだか、楽しそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s been smiling like that for a while now.\nIt looks like she’s having fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.35675414630384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_07-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（確かにアイドルが好きだと伝わる、いい笑顔だ）\n（ あの笑顔をステージで咲かせることができたら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s obvious from her wide smile that she loves idols.）\n（If only she could let that smile of hers blossom on stage.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.65675414630385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
